                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/abosan/">阿波</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-04-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书买来至少六年了，到现在才得到能把它品读完的心境。书店属于浪漫的感性的人，实体书也是。也只有对书店和出版业怀着巨大爱意的人才能写出这样的书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="513134963">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-513134963" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-513134963" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="513134963">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nwwfewx/">伊卡洛斯</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读书不仅仅只是为了书中的内容，或者说，书的内容其实并不只是那些印在纸上的文
字。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="159261403">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-159261403" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-159261403" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="159261403">有用</a>
